strategy disclosing plans to increase this years authorization by 
22 billion or 39 percent to reach the 79 billion 
the plan would authorize 16 billion for corrections 449 for 
interdiction on the international level including some 260 for 
military aid to the drugproduction countries of peru bolivia and 
colombia 350 million for state and local law enforcement 250 
million for expanding the court system 31 billion for other law 
