world 
his disdain for categories started when he was a child in austin 
texas he said 
the 60s was a good time musically because i would go to the 
store and buy a beatles record a merle haggard record a buck owens 
record and a flatt and scruggs record all on the same rack they 
didnt separate them id buy them at the grocery store 
thats why i bristle when somebody pegs it all down because i 
would easily go from country to something classical ravel to the 
rolling stones music is something to be appreciated for how it 
feels how it speaks to your heart not your mind 
crowell hooked up with emmylou harris in 1974 after she recorded 
