center for the study of new media and information technology 
these winners could be italys silvio berlusconi the west german 
leo kirch and britains robert maxwell he said in an interview 
and they have no history of producing television art burgelman 
added 
they will want to make heaps of money and will produce works 
for the largest common denominator said hamelink of the hague 
research group you will get the typical series you get in the 
united states a bit of violence a bit of mild sex 
said burgelman instead of american pulp we will have european 
pulp 
