representing 25000 of uniteds 70000 workers would invest pension 
funds in ual 
starkman said the pilots would have a difficult time running ual 
without strong support from the other unions 
what really makes this deal go or not is the cooperation of 
labor he said 
ual has said its board of directors will form a committee to 
review the bids for the company 
